title: All About Power For Radios
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

QDX & QMX require (at most) 12.0V, not 13.5V or better.  Be careful!!!
(This assumes you have wired your unit for 12V.  Similar caution applies if you wired for 9V.)

Jeff Moore makes a Low Drop Out inline power module.

